  <h2>American University- Localizing Peace Initiative</h2>

<p>
<img class="key-image" src="/images/bird.jpg"></img>
The BRIDGE Project and Localizing Peace have been collaborating since May of 2011 to showcase resources to address the question of local peace in the DC area.  Localizing Peace has contributed resources from their directory to the BRIDGE Project website, and continues to work actively to advance the discussion of local peace.
</p>

<p>
More information about the initiative can be found on their website: <br />
